'''象牙参属'''（学名：''Roscoea''）是属于[[薑科|薑科]]的一类高山植物。主要分布在[[横断山|横断山]]-东喜马拉雅一带。花大而艳丽，具有长花冠管<ref>{{cite news|title=象牙参属植物传粉生态学研究获进展|url=http://paper.sciencenet.cn/htmlpaper/201112610195237314428.shtm?id=14428|accessdate=2011-01-26|date=2011-01-26|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013552/http://paper.sciencenet.cn/htmlpaper/201112610195237314428.shtm?id=14428|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite journal|author=Z.-Q. Zhang|coauthors=W. J. Kress, W.-J. Xie, P.-Y. Ren, J.-Y. Gao, Q.-J. Li|title=Reproductive biology of two Himalayan alpine gingers (Roscoea spp., Zingiberaceae) in China: pollination syndrome and compensatory floral mechanisms|journal=Plant Biology|date=2010-12-22|doi=10.1111/j.1438-8677.2010.00423.x|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1438-8677.2010.00423.x/abstract|accessdate=2011-01-26|archive-date=2011-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004050924/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1438-8677.2010.00423.x/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

